reviewText: I mainly like the hardees commericals. still looking for farrah commercials. This Dvd can't live up too 1001 classic commericals.

My wife is a huge fan of vintage commercials, and these collections had very few duplicates. Each volume is at least 90 minutes and have many ads that we've never seen, in very clean condition. A very worthwhile purchase!

These old ads are like a trip down memory lane. How well I recall some of these very ads. Prell, Scope, Nyquil, Pampers, I love you all. These are the product pushed between those great shows, whether it be Lost in Space, Dragnet, or Hawaii 5-O. A fun time machine of memories.
I was looking for the humorous Alka Seltz'er, and Volkswagen commercials. Not a one. Mostly cigarette commercials, and many of the same brand
